rows.label: tev057601_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Jitsu about recent developments.

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0001
rows.name:
Human BLADEs giving names to places in
Nightglow Woods.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0002
rows.name:
Up until now, Nopon just used whatever name came
to mind. Very hard for Jitsu to keep track![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0003
rows.name:
Jitsu and friends are going to start using new human
names so business transactions go smoother.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0004
rows.name:
By the way, random friend said that some Noctilum
names have rather dramatic flair. Jitsu have no idea
what this mean.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0008
rows.name:
Dadapon gone and Tatsu went to live with new
friends...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0009
rows.name:
That means Jitsu going to succeed Mamapon as next
Dodonga Caravan leader![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0010
rows.name:
Probably for the best. Jitsu have way better math and
people skills than Tatsu.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0016
rows.name:
*sniff* Jitsu put everyone in danger.
Even Mamapon and little brotherpons...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0017
rows.name: Maybe Jitsu not ready to be next leader.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0018
rows.name:
Come home, Tatsu! No matter what anyone says,
Dodonga Caravan miss Tatsu![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0025
rows.name:
Deep in heart of Noctilum is special place friend
cannot reach on foot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0026
rows.name:
But friend could get there if friend grew wings...
And friend can do THAT! Jitsu believes![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0027
rows.name:
Jitsu and other Nopon friends can also fly,
but it hard work, so no one do it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0028
rows.name:
Instead, Nopon use secret passageway that only Nopon
can fit through.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0029
rows.name: Then they arrive at lovely beautiful place![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0035
rows.name:
Stinky Prone that tried to eat brotherpon Tatsu are
gone, but friend should still not let guard down.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0036
rows.name:
Plenty of dangerous critters on Mira with bigger mouths
and appetites than Prone![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0037
rows.name:
Brotherpon taking big risk getting used to urban life.
Pack on too many pounds, and Tatsu become walking
lunchbox for hungry critters![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0038
rows.name:
...Wait. If Tatsu come home, maybe Jitsu can use fat
brotherpon as decoy to catch huge caecus![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0039
rows.name:
Then Jitsu can eat meat again! Meat meat MEEEEAT!
...How long has it been?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0040
rows.name:
Meh? Where did Dadapo...er...where did
BROTHERPON Tatsu go?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057601_MSG0041
rows.name: What is Jitsu supposed to do without brotherpon?![ST:wait ]
